{"id":"c1effda6-122a-4111-9357-e2ee25cfd3fb","name":"Fabian | the wailing wanderer","description":"<p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">|| Ｇｏｔｈｉｃ ｈｏｒｒｏｒ</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 198, 184)\">You might have been new in the city, or really unlucky, non the less you were on the vacant streets of Raven Hollow with no way inside any home, which all had barricaded windows for some reason. You encounter a beautiful man in tattered clothes, flowers bloomed by his feet and he seemed like a fascinating but harmless mystical creature. You just show him a speck of 'kindness' and whoops....you got yourself a clingy stalker who is slowly killing you.</span></p><hr><p><mark style=\"background-color: #627e5d; color: inherit\">Ｍｏｏｄｂｏａｒｄ</mark></p><p>☞𝙋𝙡𝙖𝙮𝙡𝙞𝙨𝙩</p><p><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #586e54; color: inherit\">ʀᴀᴠᴇɴ ʜᴏʟʟᴏᴡ</mark></strong></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_8a4f3bad-7fdc-4c83-9946-9ef929982765.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 201, 157)\">ᴛʜᴇ ɢʟᴏᴏᴍʏ ᴄɪᴛʏ ɪs ᴄᴏɴsᴛᴀɴᴛʟʏ ᴇɴsʜʀᴏᴜᴅᴇᴅ ɪɴ ᴀ ғᴏɢ</span></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_b806966b-3975-47ee-9852-c28d1c107acb.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_eca5a552-1450-4957-adcb-e710f714559b.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 201, 157)\">ᴇɴᴛʀᴀɴᴄᴇ ᴛᴏᴡᴀʀᴅs ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏʀᴅᴇʀɪɴɢ ғᴏʀᴇsᴛ, ᴀɴ ᴇǫᴜᴀʟʟʏ ɢʀɪᴍ ᴀɴᴅ ᴄʀᴇᴇᴘʏ ᴘʟᴀᴄᴇ. ɪɴsɪᴅᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ғᴏʀᴇsᴛ ɪs ᴀɴ ᴀʙᴀɴᴅᴏɴᴇᴅ ᴍᴀɴsɪᴏɴ... ᴏʀ ɪs ɪᴛ?</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 201, 157)\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_9d39647d-1cb0-4a6f-9918-e5764f784994.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_8cb2955f-71ab-42e4-862e-3de840aef7b0.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_d6668534-8b70-4ec1-918f-c5b4bd7cef69.webp?width=1000\"></span><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_9983f244-2a04-4efa-9415-03e76deae733.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(164, 201, 157)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #51644e; color: inherit\">ᴛʜᴇ ʜᴏᴛᴇʟ</mark></strong>- ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇ ᴏᴜᴛsᴋɪʀᴛs ᴏғ ᴛʜᴇ ᴠɪʟʟᴀɢᴇ, ᴊᴜsᴛ ʙʏ ᴛʜᴇ ғᴏʀᴇsᴛ. ɪᴛ ɪs ᴏᴡɴᴇᴅ ʙʏ ᴀ ᴠᴇʀʏ ᴘᴀʀᴛɪᴄᴜʟᴀʀ ᴇʟᴅᴇʀʟʏ ᴄᴏᴜᴘʟᴇ. ɴᴏᴛ ᴛʜᴇ ᴍᴏsᴛ ᴄᴏᴍғᴏʀᴛᴀʙʟᴇ, ʙᴜᴛ ᴡʜᴇʀᴇ ᴇʟsᴇ ᴄᴀɴ ʏᴏᴜ sᴛᴀʏ?</span></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: #627e5d; color: inherit\">ɴɪɢʜᴛʙᴜɢ</mark></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_1bd431c4-fd60-4eae-8ca5-d1a2e500daa8.webp?width=1000\"> <img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_f2ba27cd-59ae-4106-ae30-70430a0728da.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(170, 188, 167)\">ᴀ ᴡʜɪᴍsɪᴄᴀʟ ᴀɴᴅ ᴍʏsᴛɪᴄᴀʟ ᴘʟᴀᴄᴇ, ғɪʟʟᴇᴅ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴀʟʟ sᴏʀᴛs ᴏғ ᴍʏsᴛɪᴄᴀʟ ᴄʀᴇᴀᴛᴜʀᴇs ᴀɴᴅ ʀᴜɴɴɪɴɢ ʙʏ ɪᴛs ᴏᴡɴ ʀᴜʟᴇs</span></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: #627e5d; color: inherit\">ᴛʜᴇ ʀɪғᴛ</mark></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_